OpenTox,is,a,framework,that,can,be,used,in,the,creation,of,predictive,toxicology,applications,It,can,be,integrated,with,other,APIs,to,provide,users,with,access,to,a,variety,of,distributed,toxicological,resources,including,data,computer,models,validation,and,reporting,OpenTox,is,working,to,meet,the,requirements,of,the,REACH,legislation,for,providing,alternatives,to,animal,experiments,for,toxicity,testing